research_municipality_step.notes: Athens, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The City Council consists of the Mayor and four City Council members, who run and serve at large. Cody Craig was sworn in as a Council Member in May 2024. While specific 'Place' assignments are provided for other council members, a 'Place' was not consistently found for Cody Craig across all sources, so he is listed without a division.
